                "Text": {
                    "JoinWith": "\n\n",
                    "Values":{
                        "0":"<speaker=_PC>Roommate? I didn't think I would have a roommate.</speaker>",
                        "1":"<speaker=_NPC1>Most girls have roommates, silly. Unless your parents pay a lot of extra money. And you surely are not one of these cases.</speaker> She laughes.",
